Jim Phelan

  · ltf11Spgonls4t5l2f6m7u5u1694906o9rg7e69hdh  ·
I would like to conduct a brief, one question survey, based on the story below.
My wife Ericka and I were recently driving on a winding mountain road. Ericka, who is 10 year younger than me, asked me how far it was to our destination. I said it was still several miles of driving, even though the destination was quite close as the crow flies. So she starts laughing and says, “As the crow flies? Where did that come from? Nobody talks like that!”
So my question is this. What the hell???
